TOLLYWOOD : UPDATEBaahubali Is Anushka's Last MovieLeaving many young hearts in disappointment, celebrated heroine Anushka Shetty is leaving for the second phase of her life. Keeping a full stop to her silver screen sizzling, the Mangalore based actress wants to dazzle in her real life as a fantastic bride and a doting wife. Check this story.While Anushka was shooting for her latest flick 'Lingaa' with Rajnikanth sometime back, an aspiring director narrated her a female-oriented story. She loved the heroine-centric script to the core but tendered a 'sorry' for the young director. And the reason to reject the flick has shocked the director. Apparently Anushka doesn't want to work in films any more as she is getting married once she wraps up shooting of 'Baahubali'. Please check if your heart is in place or not, because this news turns out to be almost true.Sources added that Anushka will be tying the knot with a businessman, who is not known to industry, and the couple might settle down in USA post their marriage.
